   <dcterms:isPartOf>Waechter ~ HSchenker</dcterms:isPartOf>
   <dc:title>Handwritten note from Eberhard von Waechter to Schenker, dated October 11, 1919</dc:title>
<dc:type>Note</dc:type>
<dcterms:created>1919-10-11T12:00:00</dcterms:created>
   <dcterms:dateSubmitted>2010-04-05</dcterms:dateSubmitted>
   <dc:description>Waechter regrets Schenker's refusal to agree to write articles for Der Merker,
    and expresses doubts about his "prophetic zeal." </dc:description>
   <dc:subject>Aufsatz; article; Publikation; publication; Verleger; publishers; Faktor; factor;
    Musikleben; musical life; korrupt; corrupt; Sache; cause; prophetischer Eifer; prophetic zeal </dc:subject>
